  "texts": [
    "At its core, RiP-PLE empowers instructors and students to collaboratively curate a wealth of high-quality learning materials.",
    "These resources then serve to tailor content recommendations to students, aligning with their individual mastery levels.",
    "Through RiPPLE, students are not just passive recipients of information but active creators, honing vital skills in content creation, critical analysis, and effective communication within a supportive community.",
    "Instructors, on the other hand, find a scalable way to enrich their courses with diverse practice materials, significantly reducing the traditional time investment required.",
    "Finally, academic departments benefit by offering customized educational experiences at minimal costs."
  ],
